[h1|PV]Proficiency Values[/h1]
[h4]Faith[/h4]
Each point in [i]Faith[/i] increases [section:clr-dc]DC[/section], [section:clr-pa]PA[/section], [section:clr-sa]SA[/section], or [section:clr-sdl]SD[/section] of any relevant spell by [section:clr-value]1[/section].
[h4]Potency[/h4]
Each point in [i]Potency[/i] increases the effects of relevant spells by [section:clr-value]1[/section], if reasonably applicable.